 can probably be removed
: what else is there? is the other stuff anomalous?

this whole section of the description up to the mention of the diary entries feels like you've copied it from a tourist brochure for the location; i can't really pinpoint exactly what's wrong but it's phrasing like  and just, the general, wordiness of it? I'd recommend editing these two paragraphs down to a couple of sentences summarising the information


